      "value": "<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg\" width=\"1407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219991/Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330556307&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219991/Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330556307&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220003\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219991\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"34596eb2-4a21-44e1-91b7-f3dcbc0ac283\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219991/Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330556307&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219991/Lama_Iridescence_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330556307&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791 1x\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"LamaIridescence-HueMapping\">Hue Mapping</h3><p><br/><strong>Target Hue</strong><br/>Maps the hues of the colors generated by the underlying physical model to the selected hues.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"e37c9125-d31a-4dfe-a979-f71211f5533d\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluence